OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine
OL,6,Fevening, with some late sunshine. Most
OL,7,Fparts staying dry overnight, however
OL,8,Fareas of low cloud and coastal mist
OL,9,Fare expected to spread westwards from
OL,10,Fthe North Sea overnight, perhaps
OL,11,Fbringing the odd spot of light drizzle.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FA cloudy start for many.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,16,FLargely dry through this period, with
OL,17,Fcloud moving inland overnight then
OL,18,Fburning away by day to sunny spells.
OL,19,FTemperatures around or a little above
OL,20,Faverage, perhaps warm at times inland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
